		<category><![CDATA[this means war]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[tom hardy]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/?p=2623</guid>
		<description>When I first saw the preview for This Means War, I thought, &amp;#8220;this could be funny.&amp;#8221;  I wasn&amp;#8217;t in any big hurry to see it at the theater, but figured it would be worth a rental.  I thought the premise was weak, but I like both Chris Pine and Tom Hardy &amp;#8211; plus Reese Witherspoon [...]</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="alignright" style="padding: 5px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;" src="http://www.chrisdoelle.com/2_movie_tix.jpg" alt="" width="116" height="91" align="left" hspace="8" />When I first saw the preview for <a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1596350/">This Means War</a>, I thought, &#8220;this could be funny.&#8221;  I wasn&#8217;t in any big hurry to see it at the theater, but figured it would be worth a rental.  I thought the premise was weak, but I like both <a href="http://www.imdb.com/name/nm1517976/">Chris Pine</a> and <a href="http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0362766/">Tom Hardy</a> &#8211; plus <a href="http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000702/">Reese Witherspoon</a> is usually a safe bet.</p>
<p>The film really didn&#8217;t even live up to my lowered expectations.  Sure, there were some decent action scenes, but the comedy was weak and the &#8220;sexiness&#8221; missed the mark often.</p>
<p><a class="highslide" onclick="return vz.expand(this)" href="http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/thismeanswar.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2628" title="This Means War" src="http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/thismeanswar.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="247" /></a></p>
<p>If you have nothing else to watch, give it a go, but don&#8217;t expect to be laughing around the water cooler with friends about it later.</p>
<p><strong>RATING 5 out of 10</strong><br />
<img src="http://www.chrisdoelle.com/goldstar.gif" alt="social media, new media titan, chris doelle, fresh media works, http://www.freshmediaworks.com" /><img src="http://www.chrisdoelle.com/goldstar.gif" alt="social media, new media titan, chris doelle, fresh media works, http://www.freshmediaworks.com" /><img src="http://www.chrisdoelle.com/goldstar.gif" alt="new media titan, chris doelle, fresh media works, http://www.freshmediaworks.com" /><img src="http://www.chrisdoelle.com/goldstar.gif" alt="new media titan, chris doelle, fresh media works, http://www.freshmediaworks.com" /><img src="http://www.chrisdoelle.com/goldstar.gif" alt="social media, new media titan, chris doelle, fresh media works, http://www.freshmediaworks.com" /></p>
]]></content:encoded>
