			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>This song has what has to be my favorite couple of lyrics of the year.   The song is Tonight, Tonight by Hot Chelle Rae.  I&#8217;ve highlighted the ones that do it for me.  Fun stuff.</p>
<blockquote><p><span style="color: #0000ff;">&#8220;It’s been a really really messed up week</span></p>
<div>
<p><span style="color: #0000ff;"> Seven days of torture, seven days of bitter</span><br />
<span style="color: #0000ff;"> And my girlfriend went and cheated on me</span><br />
<span style="color: #ff0000;"> She’s a California dime but it’s time for me to quit her</span></p>
