<p><span style="color: #0000ff;">We’re going at it tonight tonight</span><br />
<span style="color: #0000ff;"> There’s a party on the rooftop top of the world</span><br />
<span style="color: #0000ff;"> Tonight tonight and were dancing on the edge of the Hollywood sign</span><br />
<span style="color: #0000ff;"> I don’t know if I’ll make it but watch how good I’ll fake it</span><br />
<span style="color: #0000ff;"> Its all right, all right, tonight, tonight</span></p>
