<span style="color: #ff0000;"> And it kinda looks just like you</span><br />
<span style="color: #ff0000;"> Mixed with Zach Galifianakis</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #0000ff;">La la la, whatever, la la la, it doesn’t matter, la la la, oh well, la la la&#8221;</span></p>
</div>
</blockquote>
<p>Hey, any song with Zach Galifianakis is good in my book.</p>
