		<comments>http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/2011/10/09/the-myster-of-the-oh-henry-bar-is-over/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 09 Oct 2011 22:08:03 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>cdoelle@gmail.com (Chris Doelle)</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Entertainment]]></category>
