			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I have to say, he wasn&#8217;t the first person I thought if for hosting the 84th annual Academy Awards, but they could have (and have) done much worse.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/2011/02/28/oscars-pull-up-lame/">Last year</a> was horrendous and Eddie certainly has the chops to pull it off, so I am looking forward to this incarnation.</p>
<p>I expect it to be much funnier as he certainly is expert at comic timing &#8211; so even if the writing is again terrible, he won&#8217;t show it as poorly as James Franco and that other chick did last year.</p>
