		<description>Back in the mid 90&amp;#8242;s (seems like so long ago) the neighbors and I started a small run community flier/newspaper. The kids planned the paper, wrote the stories, distributed the thing &amp;#38; even sold subscriptions. It was a lot of fun and I think it really helped bring the neighborhood together. I was cleaning out [...]</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Back in the mid 90&#8242;s (seems like so long ago) the neighbors and I started a small run community flier/newspaper.  The kids planned the paper, wrote the stories, distributed the thing &amp; even sold subscriptions.  It was a lot of fun and I think it really helped bring the neighborhood together.</p>
<p>I was cleaning out some old files and came across a few of the issues.  While it appears that the first issue is lost forever, I did manage to save some.  They will be posted as I find time.</p>
