		<description>That&amp;#8217;s right.  The cycling has dropped off quite a bit in the last year &amp;#8211; it was my second lowest amount of miles ridden in a year since I started keeping track (29 years ago!) While I have already doubles last year&amp;#8217;s total, it is far from a great start.  To that end, and with [...]</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>That&#8217;s right.  The cycling has dropped off quite a bit in the last year &#8211; it was my second lowest amount of miles ridden in a year since I started keeping track (29 years ago!)</p>
<p>While I have already doubles last year&#8217;s total, it is far from a great start.  To that end, and with urging from my wife to get &#8220;back in the saddle,&#8221;  I have a chosen a ride to do that will motivate me to log the training miles.</p>
<p>Look for information on that ride very shortly &#8211; as soon as I get everything registered, scheduled and launch this latest two-wheeled campaign.</p>
<p>I am just under 500 miles short of having logged 20,000 cycling miles and feel confident I can shatter that this year.  Wish me luck and stay tuned for how you can help me out and encourage me on.</p>
