		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/?p=2336</guid>
		<description>Okay, so here is the trailer for the new Conan the Barbarian film coming out this summer. Let me say that the original comic book was one of my all-time favorites and I even liked the Schwarzenegger version of Conan, I am just not sure about Jason Momoa yet. The trailer doesn&amp;#8217;t really give enough [...]</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Okay, so here is the trailer for the new <a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0816462/">Conan the Barbarian</a> film coming out this summer.  Let me say that the original comic book was one of my all-time favorites and I even liked the <a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0082198/">Schwarzenegger version of Conan</a>, I am just not sure about <a href="http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0597388/">Jason Momoa</a> yet.</p>
<p><code>
<div><object width="499" height="281"><param name="movie" value="http://d.yimg.com/nl/movies/site/player.swf"></param><param name="flashVars" value="vid=24490513&#038;"></param><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true"></param><param name="wmode" value="transparent"></param><embed width="499" height="281" allowFullScreen="true" src="http://d.yimg.com/nl/movies/site/player.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" flashvars="vid=24490513&#038;"></embed></object></div>
<p></code></p>
<p>The trailer doesn&#8217;t really give enough information to form an opinion.  I will be looking for more previews and of course, I will be taking the boys to see it.  I just hope it doesn&#8217;t blow.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
