		<title>Day Trip to Lackland</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/RidingWithTheWindowDown/~3/N_G_qqGI8GI/</link>
		<comments>http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/2010/11/08/day-trip-to-lackland/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 09 Nov 2010 05:35:04 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>cdoelle@gmail.com (Chris Doelle)</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Entertainment]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Friends & Family]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Travel & Entertainment]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[2010]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[airshow]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[lackland afb]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[san antonio]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/?p=2264</guid>
		<description>The family took in the 2010 Lackland AFB Airshow this past weekend.  It was a lot of fun and everyone enjoyed checking out all the planes.  It was sort of a trip down memory lane for me as the last time I went to an airshow was with my father. It was way cool to [...]</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The family took in the 2010 Lackland AFB Airshow this past weekend.  It was a lot of fun and everyone enjoyed checking out all the planes.  It was sort of a trip down memory lane for me as the last time I went to an airshow was with my father.</p>
<p>It was way cool to relay information about the planes and the eras in which they flew.</p>
<p>The highlight had to be the new F-22 in action.  Holy Smoke!  This thing is amazing.  I shot a little video while there but don&#8217;t know how well it turned out yet.  Look for video when I have some free time.  For now, enjoy some photos from the outing.</p>
<p><code><object width="400" height="300"><param name="flashvars" value="offsite=true&#038;lang=en-us&#038;page_show_url=%2Fphotos%2Fshutterdog%2Fsets%2F72157625220239173%2Fshow%2F&#038;page_show_back_url=%2Fphotos%2Fshutterdog%2Fsets%2F72157625220239173%2F&#038;set_id=72157625220239173&#038;jump_to="></param><param name="movie" value="http://www.flickr.com/apps/slideshow/show.swf?v=71649"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://www.flickr.com/apps/slideshow/show.swf?v=71649" allowFullScreen="true" flashvars="offsite=true&#038;lang=en-us&#038;page_show_url=%2Fphotos%2Fshutterdog%2Fsets%2F72157625220239173%2Fshow%2F&#038;page_show_back_url=%2Fphotos%2Fshutterdog%2Fsets%2F72157625220239173%2F&#038;set_id=72157625220239173&#038;jump_to=" width="400" height="300"></embed></object></code></p>
