		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/?p=2239</guid>
		<description>&amp;#8220;I won&amp;#8217;t be wronged, I won&amp;#8217;t be insulted and I won&amp;#8217;t be laid a hand on.  I don&amp;#8217;t do these things to other people and I require the same of them.&amp;#8221; &amp;#8211; John Bernard Brooks (John Wayne in The Shootist)</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<blockquote><p><span style="font-size: medium;">&#8220;I won&#8217;t be wronged, I won&#8217;t be insulted and I won&#8217;t be laid a hand on.  I don&#8217;t do these things to other people and I require the same of them.&#8221; </span></p></blockquote>
<p>&#8211; John Bernard Brooks (John Wayne in The Shootist)</p>
