			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Okay, so most of you will either a) not have a clue what I am talking about or b) not give a flip.  I just felt that for the nerd in-the-know, I would bring them up to speed on an issue I discovered.</p>
<p>Turns out that sometime a couple months ago, I made a tweak to the website and since then &#8211; without my noticing &#8211; the feed was screwed up.</p>
<p>I still don&#8217;t know what I did, but somehow the feed itself got changed &#8211; long story short, those of you who read RWTWD in a feed reader, will suddenly notice a boatload of posts.  I guess there are times when it pays that I have been neglecting this site so much.</p>
<p>Look for the frequency to increase as I get &#8220;back in the swing&#8221; of things.</p>
<p>Peace!</p>
