		<description>This year&amp;#8217;s Tour de France is something special.  Sure, I always think that the TdF rocks, but there is something about this 100th anniversary running that is particularly exceptional. Lance is back with a new American team.  His rival, Alberto Contador is looking stronger than ever.  Andy Schleck is tough as nails and proving it [...]</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>This year&#8217;s Tour de France is something special.  Sure, I always think that the TdF rocks, but there is something about this 100th anniversary running that is particularly exceptional.</p>
<p>Lance is back with a new American team.  His rival, Alberto Contador is looking stronger than ever.  Andy Schleck is tough as nails and proving it every day (particularly in Stage 2.)   The route is quite a bit more interesting than usual&#8230; and by interesting I mean TOUGH as heck!</p>
