		<item>
		<title>My six degrees of Kevin Bacon</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/RidingWithTheWindowDown/~3/S1VHxv1IGr0/</link>
		<comments>http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/2010/05/12/my-six-degrees-of-kevin-bacon/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 13 May 2010 02:55:31 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>cdoelle@gmail.com (Chris Doelle)</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Entertainment]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Movie Reviews & TV]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[billy bob thornton]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[kevin bacon]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[merideth baxter]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[movies]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[six degrees]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/?p=2182</guid>
		<description>Okay, so I was not listed in the credits of any of these films, but I was in them. That said, I wanted to take a few seconds and list my Six Degrees of Kevin Bacon. I am sure there are more, but I thought this would be a fun start. In a movie that [...]</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/6-degrees-of-kevin-bacon-225x300.jpg" alt="" title="6-degrees-of-kevin-bacon" width="225" height="300" class="alignright size-medium wp-image-2183" />Okay, so I was not listed in the credits of any of these films, but I was in them.  That said, I wanted to take a few seconds and list my <a href="http://www-distance.syr.edu/bacon.html">Six Degrees of Kevin Bacon</a>.  I am sure there are more, but I thought this would be a fun start.</p>
<p>In a movie that had the working title, &#8220;On the Rocks&#8221; and later became called, &#8220;<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0443604/">Paradise, Texas</a>&#8221; I was shooting with Timothy Bottoms and Merideth Baxter.</p>
<p>I was also in <a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0390022/">Friday Night Lights</a> with Billy Bob Thornton and Tim McGraw.<br />
_____<br />
<strong>3 Steps</strong><br />
Chris Doelle<br />
