			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img hspace=8 src="http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/jesse-james-280394.jpg" alt="" title="Jesse James" width="150" height="211" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2161" align="right" />Is anyone else sick of the whole, &#8220;I cheated on my wife/gf/husband/etc,  so I am going to enter rehab for my addiction,&#8221; copout?  Really?  Jesse James is the latest in the line of celebs turning to rehab to clean up their tarnished image &#8211; blaming his philandering on sex addiction rather than the more likely, &#8220;I am a shit and I cheated.&#8221;</p>
