		<title>Those Cheetos folks just keep ‘em coming</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/RidingWithTheWindowDown/~3/4kTpxYaU8-s/</link>
		<comments>http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/2010/03/04/those-cheetos-folks-just-keep-em-coming/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 04 Mar 2010 19:29:38 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>cdoelle@gmail.com (Chris Doelle)</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[junk food]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[cheetos]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[chips]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Food]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[habanero]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/?p=2134</guid>
		<description>I have a history of posting on foods I find interesting. No brand has done more (well, maybe Mt. Dew) to try new things than Cheetos. Here is one of the latest from the fine folks at Lays &amp;#8211; Wild Habanero Cheetos! Alright, I didn&amp;#8217;t try them (I know I am letting you down there) [...]</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/img00257-20100303-1030.jpg" alt="" hspace="8" align="right" />I have a history of posting on foods I find interesting.  No brand has done more (well, maybe Mt. Dew) to try new things than <a href="http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/?s=cheetos">Cheetos</a>.  Here is one of the latest from the fine folks at Lays &#8211; Wild Habanero Cheetos!</p>
<p>Alright, I didn&#8217;t try them (I know I am letting you down there) but found them interesting enough to snap a quick pic.   Although the original crunch treat is still going strong after its introduction in 1948, my favorite all-time Cheetos flavors were Crunchy Nachos Cheetos from back in the late 90&#8242;s and the Cool Ranch Cheetos that died out almost instantly in 2003.  Want to see what they have created in the US over the years?  <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cheetos#USA.5B12.5D" target="_blank">Check out this Wikipedia link</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
			<wfw:commentRss>http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/2010/03/04/those-cheetos-folks-just-keep-em-coming/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
