			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Okay, maybe not brilliant &#8211; I mean it did pretty much rip off another of my all time favorites &#8211; Quantum Leap, but darn it, I like Journeyman.  Kevin McKidd is fast becoming one of those actors that turns in solid performances every time out and this short-lived scifi show was no exception.</p>
