<p>The bad news is that it was canceled just 13 episodes into the series.  The good news?  I guess its that <a href="http://www.hulu.com/journeyman">all the episodes are available to watch over at Hulu</a>.</p>
<p>Oh yeah, and <a href="http://www.hulu.com/quantum-leap">they have Quantum Leap too! </a> <img src='http://www.ridingwiththewindowdown.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' />  (for a limited time)</p>
